类 ScoreData

java.lang.Object
org.kelvinizer.game.gamewindow.ScoreData
public class ScoreData extends Object
Represents the score data for a game session, including the player's score, maximum combo, accuracy, worst hit time, and whether the player achieved a full combo (FC) or is playing a new chart. This class provides methods to format and display the score and performance statistics.
